      <title>亚德尼称，到 2025 年，中国仍“不具备投资潜力”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-03/china-is-still-uninvestable-in-2025-yardeni-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Yardeni Research 总裁 Ed Yardeni 表示，尽管政府采取措施提振经济，但中国仍然“不值得投资”。Yardeni 还告诉彭博社的“与哈斯琳达·阿明的洞察”节目，一些美国企业不再将中国视为机遇之地。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-03/china-is-still-uninvestable-in-2025-yardeni-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 06:08:55 GMT</pubDate>
